Another one of my oblivion ports that I could actually find some copyright stuff on.

Female only clothes, replaces hide armor set minus the helmet. (this one actually fits on vanilla skyrim bodies skin color, unless I screwed something up)

To install extract the data folder inside the .rar into your skyrim folder

Originals from TES4: Oblivion modders:
Boots and Clothing: Hentai/zotman12
Kneesocks and Underwear: Tona/toshizo7

The clothing is super skinny because I like skinny girls pretty much made everything skinnier than they came in, there are no weight sliders, so if you like big girls this probably isnt for u.

Theres probably a lot of bugs on this so if you find something let me know (should be better than my last release).

I originally made this out of random pieces I had in my oblivion folder so I\'m rly sorry if you made anything in this and I didn\'t mention you, or I\'m not supposed to release your stuff (but im pretty sure i got every1)

I originally intended to use another set of shoes for this but it was copyrighted.
